{"tid":1681934,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴：西班牙我回來了！","createTime":"2019-10-29T17:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T00:37:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"e5530eb676e8410aed8c6bf1ca235af744055df5","tid":1681934,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】伊巴謙莫域在個人instagram宣佈，將會前往西班牙，未知是否指重返西甲。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）今年年底將和洛杉磯銀河合約到期，球隊亦在美職季後賽被淘汰，代表伊巴在美職聯的生涯有機會就此告終。<br />\n<br />\n較早時間，38歲的伊巴於個人instagram上載了一段短片，由他自己說出：「你好西班牙，你猜甚麼事？我要回來了！」伊巴曾在2009年至2011年效力巴塞隆拿，共為巴塞上陣46次，攻入22球。<br />\n<br />\n早前伊巴已和多次球隊傳出加盟消息，如曼聯、國際米蘭、拿玻里等等。他早前曾豪言自已離開美職聯時，將沒有人再會記得這個聯賽。今年伊巴為洛杉磯銀河上陣29場攻入30球，效率超過場均1球。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"5f427b24baae5e85c8062f55547d5904d38a57ec","tid":1681934,"uid":81273,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"要去邊隊廢隊<br />\n今次準備現形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bb87b5e55df06876219c24593c6dc1182a130f","tid":1681934,"uid":125380,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"去伊巴"},{"pid":"62c752730b1165c851dc1228f909786012791dc4","tid":1681934,"uid":153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"去祖記同保方一齊廢老同盟"},{"pid":"6ff420d69c2ff709e691d9299f2a4388365f0f4c","tid":1681934,"uid":16659,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"29場攻入30球 雖然係美職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee8f66cc1f5d1dcbe8b2def060aa11b6d781671","tid":1681934,"uid":7854,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"美職銀河可以收得皮了 懷念主場銀河半場cashed<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2282109506b7e33d0ea9aecf0a1f6c7fd9377e5","tid":1681934,"uid":81783,"like":47,"dislike":5,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":